OL,3,C'I don't want anymore words': Victim
OL,4,Cof infected blood scandal calls for
OL,5,Caction
OL,7,FA victim of the infected blood scandal
OL,8,Fhas told ITV Meridian she is 'fed up'
OL,9,Fof all the words and just wants to get
OL,10,Fon with her life.
OL,12,FJoanne Vincent, from Worthing, was
OL,13,Fdiagnosed with cirrhosis of the liver
OL,14,Fafter she was unknowingly given
OL,15,Fcontaminated blood.
OL,17,FThe blood was infected with Hepatitis
OL,18,FC, and it took her 27 years to find
OL,19,Fout exactly what had happened to her.
