OL,3,C'I don't want anymore words': Victim
OL,4,Cof infected blood scandal calls for
OL,5,Caction
OL,7,FSpeaking following the conclusion of
OL,8,Fan inquiry into the scandal, , Joanne
OL,9,Ftold ITV Meridian she wants action.
OL,11,F" I don't want any more words", she
OL,12,Fsaid. "Words aren't going to do
OL,13,Fanything. I want action. I want
OL,14,Fclosure. I want justice. I want to get
OL,15,Fon with the rest of my life.
OL,17,F"And every day for me, I've got
OL,18,Fcirrhosis of the liver because I had
OL,19,Fcontaminated blood for 27 years before
OL,20,FI knew about it and was told I had
OL,21,FHepatitis C.
