OL,7,F"Because I've had it for so long, I've
OL,8,Fgot cirrhosis of the liver. And every
OL,9,Fday that I wake up, I think, is today
OL,10,Fthe day I'm going to have liver cancer?
OL,12,F"(I think) is today the day that I'm
OL,13,Fgoing to be told? These are liver
OL,14,Fpalms and I showed these the other
OL,15,Fday. It's really important because
OL,16,Fthis is a sign of liver damage."
