OL,3,C'I don't want anymore words': Victim
OL,4,Cof infected blood scandal calls for
OL,5,Caction
OL,7,FThe long-awaited report released on
OL,8,FMonday revealed the risks were "well-
OL,9,Fknown" decades before the infected
OL,10,Fblood products were used on patients
OL,11,Fin the UK.
OL,13,FThe scandal happened in the 1970s and
OL,14,F1980s, and after decades of
OL,15,Fcampaigning for justice, victims, and
OL,16,Ftheir families are finally getting
OL,17,Fanswers in a milestone report.
