OL,3,C'I don't want anymore words': Victim
OL,4,Cof infected blood scandal calls for
OL,5,Caction
OL,7,FHowever, despite the report
OL,8,Facknowledging the concerns of those
OL,9,Fgiven contaminated blood, Joanne says
OL,10,Fit doesn't go far enough.
OL,12,FShe fears there are nearly 2,000
OL,13,Fpeople who still don't know they were
OL,14,Fgiven contaminated blood, and says
OL,15,Faction is needed now. She said:
OL,16,F"Another really important thing that I
OL,17,Fwant to say about today is what I want
OL,18,Ffrom the report is to find the missing
OL,19,F1, 750 people that are still walking
OL,20,Faround.
